headline: JPM downgrades International Paper, says investor hopes for 2027 look too high
summary: Investing.com -- JP Morgan downgraded International Paper to Neutral from Overweight, warning that earnings expectations for both 2025 and 2027 appear too optimistic following a weaker-than-expected second quarter.
